1. Always replace list or arraylist with array.
2. Declare an arbitrary value for the array size, like I do 30 for CartItem and OrderItem
3. Use descriptive naming. Replace "conn" with "connection", "rs" with "resultset".
4. Remove the pchub.{something}, import the class package directly instead
5. The database used for this project is MySQL
6. Always use ConsoleUtils printHeader function for printing menu header.
7. Always use ConsoleUtils input function to get user input.
8. All the IDs for each table are String. It will be left padded with "0", like "C0001" for customer ID.
9. Always check the database schema when you need to generate code related to database operation / dao.